<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/shop.css" />
        <script src="/iconify/iconify.min.js"></script>
        <title>Exacube — Nos services</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <main id="services-page">

            <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
            <section id="services-hero">
                <div class="services-hero-bg">
                    <div class="sh-grid"></div>
                    <div class="sh-glow"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="services-hero-content">
                    <span class="section-label">
                        <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:store-outline"></span>
                        Nos services
                    </span>
                    <h1 class="services-hero-title">Choisissez votre <span class="services-hero-accent">formule</span></h1>
                    <p class="services-hero-desc">Hébergement Minecraft gratuit à vie ou infrastructure sur mesure — on a ce qu'il faut.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ═══ PLANS ═══ -->
            <section id="services-plans">
                <div class="services-container">
                    <div class="services-plans-grid">

                        <!-- GRATUIT -->
                        <div class="splan-card splan-featured">
                            <div class="splan-badge">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:star"></span> Populaire
                            </div>
                            <div class="splan-header">
                                <div class="splan-icon">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:gift-outline"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h2 class="splan-name">Gratuit</h2>
                                    <p class="splan-tagline">Pour toujours, sans conditions</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="splan-price">
                                <span class="splan-amount">0€</span>
                                <span class="splan-period">pour toujours</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="splan-desc">Parfait pour débuter et jouer avec tes amis sans dépenser un centime.</p>
                            <ul class="splan-features">
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="streamline-freehand:memory-computer-ram"></span>
                                    <span>3 Go de RAM</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="streamline-freehand:microprocessor-computer-chip-flash"></span>
                                    <span>2 cœurs CPU</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="cbi:seagate-ssd"></span>
                                    <span>16 Go de stockage SSD</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="la:users"></span>
                                    <span>Slots joueurs illimités</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="codicon:server-process"></span>
                                    <span>Panel Custom inclus</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:server-shield"></span>
                                    <span>Protection DDoS</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:web"></span>
                                    <span>Domaine offert</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:backup-restore"></span>
                                    <span>Backups automatiques</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:map-marker-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Hébergé en France 🇫🇷</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-limit">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:minus-circle-outline"></span>
                                    <span>1 serveur par compte</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <a href="/services/free-server" class="splan-btn splan-btn-primary">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:rocket-launch-outline"></span>
                                Commencer gratuitement
                            </a>
                        </div>

                        <!-- PRIVATE NODE -->
                        <div class="splan-card">
                            <div class="splan-header">
                                <div class="splan-icon">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:server-network"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h2 class="splan-name">Private Node</h2>
                                    <p class="splan-tagline">Réseau multi-serveurs privé</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="splan-price">
                                <span class="splan-from">à partir de</span>
                                <span class="splan-amount">4,99€</span>
                                <span class="splan-period">/ mois</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="splan-desc">Un réseau privé de serveurs interconnectés via BungeeCord, pour les projets ambitieux.</p>
                            <ul class="splan-features">
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="uil:servers"></span>
                                    <span>2 à 8 serveurs inclus</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="fa6-solid:hexagon-nodes-bolt"></span>
                                    <span>Serveur BungeeCord dédié</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="simple-icons:privateinternetaccess"></span>
                                    <span>Réseau inter-serveurs privé</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="codicon:server-process"></span>
                                    <span>Panel Custom inclus</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:server-shield"></span>
                                    <span>Protection DDoS avancée</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:backup-restore"></span>
                                    <span>Backups automatiques</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="fluent:person-support-32-filled"></span>
                                    <span>Support prioritaire</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:map-marker-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Hébergé en France 🇫🇷</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <a href="/services/private-node" class="splan-btn splan-btn-ghost">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:arrow-right"></span>
                                Voir les formules
                            </a>
                        </div>

                        <!-- CUSTOM METAL -->
                        <div class="splan-card splan-gold">
                            <div class="splan-header">
                                <div class="splan-icon splan-icon-gold">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:chip"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h2 class="splan-name">Custom Metal</h2>
                                    <p class="splan-tagline">Infrastructure 100% sur mesure</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="splan-price">
                                <span class="splan-amount splan-amount-custom">Sur mesure</span>
                                <span class="splan-period">selon tes besoins</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="splan-desc">Tu choisis chaque composant avec un technicien. L'infrastructure taillée exactement pour toi.</p>
                            <ul class="splan-features">
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:tune-vertical"></span>
                                    <span>Ressources 100% sur mesure</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:account-wrench-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Configuration avec un technicien</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:server-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Matériel dédié</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:account-group-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Idéal grands réseaux & communautés</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="fluent:person-support-32-filled"></span>
                                    <span>Support & suivi dédié</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:map-marker-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Hébergé en France 🇫🇷</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="sf-ok">
                                    <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:tag-outline"></span>
                                    <span>Prix défini selon les choix</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <a href="/services/custom-metal" class="splan-btn splan-btn-gold">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:message-outline"></span>
                                Nous contacter
                            </a>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ═══ ADD-ONS ═══ -->
            <section id="services-addons">
                <div class="services-container">

                    <div class="addons-header">
                        <span class="section-label">
                            <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:puzzle-plus-outline"></span>
                            Options à la carte
                        </span>
                        <h2 class="addons-title">Personnalise ton serveur</h2>
                        <p class="addons-subtitle">Ajoute des ressources à la demande, sans changer de plan.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="addons-grid">

                        <div class="addon-card">
                            <div class="addon-icon">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="streamline-freehand:memory-computer-ram"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="addon-body">
                                <h3>RAM supplémentaire</h3>
                                <p>Augmente la mémoire allouée pour des performances optimales avec plus de plugins ou de joueurs connectés.</p>
                                <div class="addon-price">
                                    <span class="addon-amount">0,99€</span>
                                    <span class="addon-unit">/ Go / mois</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <a href="/dashboard" class="addon-btn">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:plus"></span> Ajouter
                            </a>
                        </div>

                        <div class="addon-card">
                            <div class="addon-icon">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="cbi:seagate-ssd"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="addon-body">
                                <h3>Stockage SSD</h3>
                                <p>Étends le stockage pour plus de worlds, de sauvegardes et de fichiers de mods sans limite.</p>
                                <div class="addon-price">
                                    <span class="addon-amount">0,49€</span>
                                    <span class="addon-unit">/ Go / mois</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <a href="/dashboard" class="addon-btn">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:plus"></span> Ajouter
                            </a>
                        </div>

                        <div class="addon-card">
                            <div class="addon-icon">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:ethernet"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="addon-body">
                                <h3>Port supplémentaire</h3>
                                <p>Requis pour certains plugins : ItemsAdder, BlueMap, Dynmap, plugin de vote, cartes web navigateur.</p>
                                <div class="addon-price">
                                    <span class="addon-amount">0,49€</span>
                                    <span class="addon-unit">/ port / mois</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <a href="/dashboard" class="addon-btn">
                                <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:plus"></span> Ajouter
                            </a>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <p class="addons-note">
                        <span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:information-outline"></span>
                        Les add-ons sont disponibles depuis ton panel après inscription. Résiliables à tout moment.
                    </p>

                </div>
            </section>

        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </body>
</html>